notes: As of May 2, North Dakota is reporting people tested. On 5/3, ND began providing counts of deaths for lab-confirmed individuals with death records still pending, and lab-confirmed individuals who died but not due to COVID. As of 7/1, we have edited our figures to exclude these numbers from our death counts, resulting in an apparent drop from 24 deaths on 5/2 to 16 on 5/3.
name: North Dakota
